99. She puts spoon on the CHAIR. 
A. Did she put the fork on the chair? 
B. Did she put the spoon on the chair? 
C. Who put the spoon on the chair? 
D. Who took the spoon on the chair? 
 
100. ASA is a lawyer 
A. Is Asa a robber? 
B. Who is a lawyer? 
C. Is Asa the lawyer? 
D. Was Asa the lawyer?
